{"tid":735036,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有靈體 唔好望防煙門  外賣員接恐怖Order　客人：上樓要戴護身符","createTime":"2018-07-09T07:07:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T14:51:09.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2fecedf0164cb0e480aa4db56bfcbfee8b76bd63","tid":735036,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T07:07:53.000Z","msg":"外賣員接恐怖Order　客人：上樓要戴護身符<br />\n07月09日(一) 13:49更新 11:22建立<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180709/photo/bkn-20180709112227389-0709_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180709134919\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180709%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180709112227389-0709_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180709134919&h=72bacb90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鬼節未到都咁猛？網上流傳一張外賣送餐紙，顯示有食客在備註一欄聲稱該樓層「有靈體」，提醒外賣員「必須佩戴護身符」！ <br />\n<br />\n據該張外賣紙顯示，送餐地點為九龍藍田平田邨平旺樓一個單位，點餐時間為上周六（7日）深夜時分。據備註一欄所寫，「此地址層樓有靈體，備註外賣員不必要看防煙門、後樓梯。最好必須唸經帶護身符前來，免得日後遭遇麻煩。」 <br />\n<br />\n點餐紙似是惡作劇，而翻查資料，平旺樓去年發生過命案。2017年9月21日，一名56歲男子疑因感情問題，留下遺書後在單位內燒炭自殺。 <br />\n---------------"},{"pid":"3cfaa21a577175454d26a0545428de6f4d37c52e","tid":735036,"uid":61484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T07:09:26.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"3d5b302fca8356b985680017b8c057b72e8f3b94","tid":735036,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T07:09:28.000Z","msg":"玩鳩d M記仔就岩 成日咁臭串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3336ecb5b78a3d8b5664fcba3f679464afe8609d","tid":735036,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T07:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf47f14f767ec40c75a742438b7c52fff385c7fb","tid":735036,"uid":113626,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T07:13:30.000Z","msg":"有無確實地址? 想放工去見識下<br />\n利申: 毒撚, 我唔信隻鬼唔會調頭走 <img src=\"/a